<title>USA: Citizens Utilities sets stock dividend.</title>
<headline>Citizens Utilities sets stock dividend.</headline>
<dateline>STAMFORD, Conn. 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Citizens Utilities Co said its board of directors set a 1.6 percent third-quarter stock dividend on the company's outstanding Series A and Series B common stock.</p>
<p>The stock dividend is payable September 30 to shareholders of record on September 3, Citizens Utilities said.</p>
<p>The company said the stock dividend has a cash equivalent of 18-5/8 cents.</p>
<p>Citizens Utilities said the stock dividend rates for the first three quarters of 1996 totalled 4.8 percent, compared with 4.6 percent for the 1995 corresponding period.</p>
